RIYADH: The Avenues, a Kuwait-based shopping mall, is planning to expand into Saudi Arabia in the next four years. It will launch two outlets in Riyadh and Alkhobar, said Khalid Al-Shariaan, CEO of Al-Mabanee, the company that operates the mall.
	The design for Riyadh is now complete and the contract is expected to be awarded soon while work on Alkhobar project has already begun, Al-Shariaan told Al Arabiya.